================================================================================
Bundled third-party components
================================================================================

The `packages/` directory contains unmodified source tarballs of Bioconductor R
packages, redistributed here solely to enable offline installation of AutoCen's
tandem-repeat dependency TRASH (https://github.com/vlothec/TRASH_2) on hosts with
limited internet access. These packages are NOT part of AutoCen and retain their
own copyright and license. Each is distributed under the Artistic License 2.0
(https://opensource.org/license/artistic-2-0); zlibbioc additionally bundles zlib
under the zlib license.

  Package             Version    License        Source
  ------------------  ---------  -------------  --------------------------------
  BiocGenerics        0.52.0     Artistic-2.0   Bioconductor
  Biostrings          2.74.1     Artistic-2.0   Bioconductor
  GenomeInfoDb        1.42.3     Artistic-2.0   Bioconductor
  GenomeInfoDbData    1.2.15     Artistic-2.0   Bioconductor
  IRanges             2.40.1     Artistic-2.0   Bioconductor
  S4Vectors           0.44.0     Artistic-2.0   Bioconductor
  UCSC.utils          1.2.0      Artistic-2.0   Bioconductor
  XVector             0.46.0     Artistic-2.0   Bioconductor
  zlibbioc            1.52.0     Artistic-2.0   Bioconductor

These tarballs are the official releases obtained from Bioconductor
(https://bioconductor.org) and have not been altered. To obtain them from the
original source instead, use BiocManager::install() within R.
